Responsibilities:
Work closely with Field Sales and Product Support (Application & Engineering) staff to support Marine applications.
Conduct technical review of specific certification requirements for Marine applications with strong connections to Marine services.
Ensure compliance to all department operating procedures and execute initiatives to improve internal process.
Conduct export compliance screening according to the Quality Management System procedures.
Meet customers to discuss on scheduling and project management issues.
Requirements:
Degree in Engineering with minimum 2 years experience in the Marine industry.
Previous experience in the Marine industry, focusing on internal processes/order flow/processes will be preferred.
Possess good business acumen, strong analytical, problem solving and decision making skills.
Customer orientated with good interpersonal and communication skills.